# 7. **Housing Market — The Hidden Transmission Channel**

![Image](https://www.morningstar.com.au/_ipx/f_webp%26q_100/https%3A//cloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com/morningstar/RXDBNPKOHVQU7QA7MLBIRXJ4AU.jpg?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

![Image](https://cdn.metropole.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/fig003.jpg?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

### Why it matters:

* Australia has high household debt
* Mostly variable mortgage rates
* Households respond *very quickly* to rate changes
* RBA rate hikes = almost immediate consumption slowdown

### Trades:

* Slowdown → **Receive 2Y swaps**, curve **steepener**
* Housing boom → **Short 10Y bonds** (growth & wealth effects)

